用嚟服務市民嘅權力 嚟傷害市民 先會比全世界反<br />\n<br />\n叫班孽種自己問心 612班人渣有幾多打市民係因為純粹火起 喪失理智 屌你老味就算比盡你當真係鎮壓 咁撚多警犬屌人老母 亂鳩打人 攻撃記者 仲要笑得出 無私怨嘅警犬會咁做???想服務市民嘅警犬會咁做???<br />\n<br />\n依家直頭講撚到唔幫市民??? 咁要警察嚟到底係做乜柒??? 直接啲講句 如果你做警察嘅目的 唔撚係為市民服務 而係真係當&ldquo;打份工啫&rdquo; 咁你都係仆街死左佢啦"},{"pid":"b0d1514f8dc32b1d69ad7cb32be070ea51bfbab8","tid":1220870,"uid":135040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T08:00:44.000Z","msg":"而加啲野擺上網仲有用過報警啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我成世人好似， 次警都未報過，都唔知有乜用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae44120b4c56924f4c20641aaf0f07ab189ee879","tid":1220870,"uid":31257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T08:01:45.000Z","msg":"毅進仔唔識分莊閒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34322ad3ef71e00d3f51b032a767ed2aa279658b","tid":1220870,"uid":127833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"729bcea323ebd6061ffc7618acd6eecb5afa91eb","tid":1220870,"uid":38143,"like":667,"dislike":2,"score":665,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T05:44:46.000Z","msg":"夠薑唔好出糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T08:04:31.000Z","msg":"夠薑唔好著裝出黎做野，d裝備唔好買比狗著既"},{"pid":"b0042f26a6f34c95f847a213641aeccdd10b20a3","tid":1220870,"uid":99055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T08:05:40.000Z","msg":"以後喺街見到警犬請大聲屌佢老母"},{"pid":"384accb0ca3237d5c47800e4ff86276618881dc9","tid":1220870,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T08:07:22.000Z","msg":"發夢有公務員講：FAX去公務員事務局投訴，警察會無得撈，無退休金，仲要坐監<br />\n公務員事務局<br />\n傳 真 : 2868 5069<br />\n電 郵 : csbcomp@csb.gov.hk<br />\n<br />\n以下係夢境資料，隱約記得：<br />\n1. 投訴警察開槍, 過份使用武力, 執法不公, FAX + EMAIL, 之後會有人跟進, 勁過警監會好多, 未過試用期警察多數88加刑事 , 舊制既公務員隨時連退休金都無埋<br />\n2. 必須寫清楚警察名同編號 (用呢條link查<a href=\"https://police-github.github.io/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpolice-github.github.io%2F&d=yztsqsfTIdfogAH81g8uWJMONXnVHdpXbsFGehQCOpI%3D&h=42f5eb0e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://police-github.github.io/</a>)<br />\n3. 要用正式方法送佢地一程, Fax + email 最好, Email 補資料, 呢個直接影響升遷甚至炒人，要開board, 唔好用1823<br />\n4. 可以叫議員寫仲快處理, 列為Urgent 處理"},{"pid":"837f04d7292db8b72285c2216ef9194be1638c27","tid":1220870,"uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T08:08:55.000Z","msg":"梗係要報，仲要報多啲添，事無大小都要報。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d16a7b300396c97031448588462ec93ca173d37b","tid":1220870,"uid":65074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T08:08:57.000Z","msg":"佢又唔係好心幫我，佢返工咋，返工唔做野等收投訴啦"},{"pid":"b20a1bd2eddd3890364ed9af651e1ca023b38500","tid":1220870,"uid":76609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T08:09:02.000Z","msg":"老細有出糧俾你，俾人鬧係人工嘅一部份<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41f9400c6777bca22e0fa114dd986d7bbe5e856a","tid":1220870,"uid":148987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T08:09:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ff9d8bf80be5ae025352ddc58e04a30792018d0","tid":1220870,"uid":5809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T08:10:26.000Z","msg":"警察以後唔出糧，我以後唔報警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8fad4418f230b284c1259c4f2fabc084583c00d","tid":1220870,"uid":95,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e65592c9174c439b71fde3a4d55bbc4c65857f94","tid":1220870,"uid":111354,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"8545e565e10496ba5980156bab4a3e50ca03b2ba","tid":1220870,"uid":111354,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T06:25:02.000Z","msg":"香港警察誓詞<br